description: Sun-filled top floor 1 bed 1.5 bath in the true heart of South Boston. Enjoy living just steps from everything Southie has to offer, including numerous restaurants, shops, the beach and MBTA bus lines. Upon entering through your private staircase, you're greeted by high ceilings, a bright skylight, and hardwood floors. The open concept living space comes with tons of built in storage space and room for working from home, along with an eat-in kitchen and convenient half bath. The bedroom is nice and quiet in the back of the unit and boasts an en-suite bathroom. Central air, in-unit laundry, and a private back deck off the kitchen makes for the perfect home. Excellent opportunity for first time home buyers and has great rental income for investors.
